{"word":"πλάτος","slug":"πλάτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πλάτος</b></el> <el>(πλάτος, ος, εος, τό,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>πλᾰτύς</el>\n<p/><i>breadth, width</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:— <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <el>πλάτος</el> or <el>τὸ πλ.</el>, <i>in breadth</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/>"}]}